com.intel.fightclub.dialog.observer

Class WorkoutSessionObserver

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.observer.EventObserver<WorkoutSessionObserver.WorkoutInfo>
      • com.intel.fightclub.dialog.observer.WorkoutSessionObserver

  • @ThreadSafe
public final class WorkoutSessionObserver
extends EventObserver<WorkoutSessionObserver.WorkoutInfo>
    Cache for WorkoutStateUpdates provided by ARDA during a workout in progress. This will enable us to query things such as the current phase in real time.
